00:19:24,380 --> 00:19:25,655
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Chuan, famous thinker forced into exile in Japan for participating in the "Second Revolution" against Yuan Shikai]
You'll scare Junman back home!

415
00:19:25,655 --> 00:19:25,803
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Chuan, famous thinker forced into exile in Japan for participating in the "Second Revolution" against Yuan Shikai]

416
00:19:25,803 --> 00:19:26,621
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Chuan, famous thinker forced into exile in Japan for participating in the "Second Revolution" against Yuan Shikai]
Hurry back!

417
00:19:26,621 --> 00:19:26,861
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Chuan, famous thinker forced into exile in Japan for participating in the "Second Revolution" against Yuan Shikai]

418
00:19:26,861 --> 00:19:28,417
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Chuan, famous thinker forced into exile in Japan for participating in the "Second Revolution" against Yuan Shikai]
Cut your hair, take a bath and change your clothes.

419
00:19:28,417 --> 00:19:28,548
Cut your hair, take a bath and change your clothes.

420
00:19:28,864 --> 00:19:29,843
There's a bath

421
00:19:30,039 --> 00:19:31,710
and there is only one change of clothes.

422
00:19:32,137 --> 00:19:32,654
Alright.

423
00:19:32,899 --> 00:19:34,539
Zhong Fu, wait!

424
00:19:39,219 --> 00:19:41,107
It's windy at sea. Take care of yourself.

425
00:19:46,334 --> 00:19:49,334
Okay, I'll be glad to do so.

426
00:19:50,616 --> 00:19:53,832
Shou Chang, I owe you three favours today.

427
00:19:54,151 --> 00:19:56,339
In the future, you must remember to ask for it.

428
00:19:56,501 --> 00:19:57,320
What are they?

429
00:19:57,495 --> 00:19:59,135
One is to help me get out of trouble.

430
00:19:59,265 --> 00:20:00,591
Second is to lend me clothes.

431
00:20:01,015 --> 00:20:01,896
And the third?

432
00:20:02,265 --> 00:20:03,495
I ate your food.

433
00:20:06,834 --> 00:20:07,980
But I had enough to eat before

434
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:09,175
before it knocked me off my feet.

435
00:20:09,551 --> 00:20:10,820
So keep rubbing it in.

436
00:20:11,201 --> 00:20:12,370
Can I buy you all dinner?

437
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:13,415
We haven't even eaten yet.

438
00:20:14,019 --> 00:20:14,904
Then we'll follow the trail.

439
00:20:15,186 --> 00:20:16,334
Good, Brother Zhong Fu, this way.

440
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:42,486
Zhong Fu, what time is it already, you're still not going to sleep?

441
00:20:44,314 --> 00:20:45,743
What is there worth seeing outside?

442
00:20:46,071 --> 00:20:48,271
The boat passed Shandong.

443
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:51,543
I feel apprehensive as I near home.

444
00:20:52,743 --> 00:20:54,429
The boat passed Shandong.

445
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:57,957
There's anger in my heart. I want to scold someone.

446
00:20:59,443 --> 00:21:00,971
I want to scold Yuan Shikai.

447
00:21:04,643 --> 00:21:06,371
I also want to scold this Yuan Datou.

448
00:21:07,943 --> 00:21:09,371
I don't know what he's thinking,

449
00:21:09,857 --> 00:21:11,800
he dared to give Qingdao to Japan.

450
00:21:12,386 --> 00:21:14,529
You say, did this guy take the wrong medicine?

451
00:21:17,643 --> 00:21:19,457
Yuan Shikai did not take the wrong medicine.

452
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,600
It's our country

453
00:21:22,271 --> 00:21:23,586
that is already incurable.

454
00:21:25,143 --> 00:21:25,843
Why do you say that?

455
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:27,200
Think about it.

456
00:21:27,557 --> 00:21:29,943
From guangnian, when Lin Zexu forbid opium.

457
00:21:30,364 --> 00:21:32,471
It's been a whole 75 years already.

458
00:21:33,257 --> 00:21:34,518
In the middle of this, how many people

459
00:21:34,645 --> 00:21:35,900
thought of different ways

460
00:21:35,982 --> 00:21:38,236
but still couldn't save the Great Qing Dynasty

461
00:21:38,371 --> 00:21:41,400
Sun Zhongshan introduced the republic from the West,

462
00:21:41,871 --> 00:21:43,557
people of the country all thought that this

463
00:21:43,558 --> 00:21:45,171
was a remedy to save the country and enrich the people.

464
00:21:45,443 --> 00:21:48,343
Who would have thought, the republic works in other countries

465
00:21:48,857 --> 00:21:50,514
but inside of China it does not work anymore.

466
00:21:51,257 --> 00:21:52,700
Three to four years of the republic later,

467
00:21:53,886 --> 00:21:55,414
the country is not as good as it used to be.

468
00:21:56,357 --> 00:21:57,771
Since there is no cure,

469
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:59,614
then isn't taking the old way better.

470
00:21:59,871 --> 00:22:02,257
These aren't just the thoughts of one or two people.

471
00:22:02,629 --> 00:22:03,357
Bai Sha

472
00:22:03,657 --> 00:22:04,529
Isn't it?

473
00:22:04,871 --> 00:22:08,900
Right now Liang Shiyi and his group

474
00:22:09,271 --> 00:22:11,971
are establishing connections everywhere, moving up and down,

475
00:22:13,214 --> 00:22:15,400
joining Yang Hugong, Yan Jidao

476
00:22:15,614 --> 00:22:17,829
and helping a villain blindly create disturbances.

477
00:22:19,291 --> 00:22:20,686
Unreasonable.

478
00:22:22,829 --> 00:22:24,729
Yang Du, Yan Fu

479
00:22:25,529 --> 00:22:28,043
(idiom) they are the wisest who can have a momentary lapse in judgement,

480
00:22:28,871 --> 00:22:30,843
whereas that Liang Shiyi group

481
00:22:31,057 --> 00:22:33,771
are political hooligans with no moral bottom line.

482
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,829
I made up a name for them

483
00:22:35,871 --> 00:22:37,171
called "courtesy"

484
00:22:38,729 --> 00:22:41,100
Li Yi Lian, what does it mean?

485
00:22:42,643 --> 00:22:45,529
Courtesy: shameless

486
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:49,714
Extremely shameless! Especially shameless!

487
00:22:50,386 --> 00:22:52,857
Good! What a good courtesy!

488
00:22:55,471 --> 00:22:58,543
Zhong Fu, your thinking is clearly unusual!

489
00:23:02,214 --> 00:23:04,757
Bai Sha, I'm ashamed.

490
00:23:05,771 --> 00:23:07,114
It's been more than ten years.

491
00:23:07,343 --> 00:23:09,714
Chen Duxiu first learned Kang Liang,

492
00:23:09,929 --> 00:23:11,357
followed by Zhong Shan,

493
00:23:11,871 --> 00:23:13,300
committed to the political revolution,

494
00:23:13,529 --> 00:23:15,657
running this way and that way escaping death many times.

495
00:23:16,043 --> 00:23:17,743
Five trips to Japan alone.

496
00:23:18,086 --> 00:23:19,171
The results until now,

497
00:23:19,271 --> 00:23:20,957
they still haven't achieved anything right?

498
00:23:21,457 --> 00:23:23,014
China's matters,

499
00:23:23,157 --> 00:23:24,471
by relying on political revolution,

500
00:23:24,971 --> 00:23:26,800
doesn't solve the fundamental problem.

501
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:30,400
To get to the bottom of this, we must change our way of thinking.

502
00:23:31,529 --> 00:23:32,929
Do you have any new ideas?

503
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,457
I don't dare to say my new ideas.

504
00:23:34,771 --> 00:23:35,800
On my return this time,

505
00:23:36,771 --> 00:23:37,857
I've made up my mind.

506
00:23:39,129 --> 00:23:41,057
For 20 years, I'm not going to touch politics.

507
00:23:41,871 --> 00:23:43,657
If you're not going to touch politics, then what do you want to do?

508
00:23:44,143 --> 00:23:48,086
Transform myself. Replace the person, replace the brain.

509
00:23:48,714 --> 00:23:49,729
It's not early anymore.

510
00:23:50,957 --> 00:23:51,971
Hurry up and go to sleep.

511
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:56,514
Zhong Fu what time is it already?

512
00:23:56,857 --> 00:23:58,000
What are you still sitting there for?

513
00:23:58,100 --> 00:23:59,271
It's so dark out there,

514
00:23:59,329 --> 00:24:00,343
you can't see anything at all.

515
00:24:00,344 --> 00:24:10,300
Sleep. Turn off the lights, okay?

516
00:24:11,414 --> 00:24:14,700
I do see.

